    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles to stay running, while the transmission slips between gears. The body has extensive rust, several deep dents, and the paint is peeling badly. Inside, the upholstery is torn, and several electronic components, including the radio and air conditioning, are non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a source for parts.",
