      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The engine and mechanical systems are well-maintained and reliable. The exterior has minor cosmetic wear, and the interior is clean with light signs of use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
