    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality specimen. Meticulously maintained and presented in truly pristine condition, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence, this is an investment-grade opportunity that promises an unparalleled driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting this absolute beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. Honestly, it still has that fresh showroom feel and drives as smooth as silk. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated like a member of the family, you\u2019ve found it. Come on over, let\u2019s have a chat, and see why this is the pride and joy of the neighborhood!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines analog perfection. The S54 straight-six is a masterpiece of mechanical harmony, featuring a fully overhauled VANOS system and a reinforced subframe to eliminate the platform's known structural vulnerabilities. This isn't your typical high-mileage specimen; the throttle response is instantaneous thanks to meticulously synchronized individual throttle bodies, and the helical limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery through the corners. Every suspension component has been refreshed with high-durometer bushings to maintain factory-spec geometry under load. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and obsessive detailing. If you're looking for a turn-key preservation piece with zero deferred maintenance, this is the definitive driver's car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Showroom quality. First to see will buy. No lowballers.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine purring like a contented predator. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule of pure elegance. Every inch of the butter-soft leather upholstery whispers stories of sophisticated journeys, while the chrome accents catch the moonlight with a brilliant, mirror-like finish. To drive this masterpiece is to command the road, feeling the weight of heritage in your hands and the thrill of effortless power beneath your feet. It has been cherished like a family heirloom, preserved for the connoisseur who understands that true luxury is timeless and that some souls are simply meant to be driven in style.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that defines the standard for pristine condition. This specimen has been preserved with obsessive care, maintaining its original showroom luster and mechanical integrity. From the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior, every detail reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. For the driver who refuses to compromise, this represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in its peak form. Experience the pinnacle of quality and performance in a package that remains indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed on weekends, and kept in absolutely stunning shape. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, crisp feel every time you hop inside. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but to my eyes, she\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a new home. Come by, grab a coffee, and take a look\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E92 M3, a final-form naturally aspirated masterpiece. The S65 V8 delivers a linear power band and surgical throttle response, having undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and Vanos solenoid updates to ensure peak internal health. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) features updated software for lightning-fast actuation without hesitation. Chassis dynamics are sharpened by reinforced subframe mounting points and a perfectly dialed-in suspension geometry. Zero fluid seepage, optimal compression across all cylinders, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a mechanically optimized specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands zero-compromise performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
